		<!-- Two -->
		<section id="two" class="wrapper style3 fade-up">
			<div class="inner">
				<h2>What we do</h2>
				<p>SkillShare Connect bridges the gap between volunteers, non-profits, and businesses by creating a platform where skilled individuals can offer their expertise to causes that matter. Whether you're a volunteer looking to make a difference or an organization seeking help, we’re here to connect you.</p>
				<div class="features">
					<section>
						<span class="icon solid major fa-code"></span>
						<h3>How It Works</h3>
						<ol>
							<li>Volunteers: Create your profile, list your skills, and showcase your availability.</li>
							<li>Opportunities: Organizations can post available opportunities for volunteers.</li>
							<li>Smart Matching: We automatically connect volunteers with opportunities based on skills and location using our intelligent matching system and Google Maps integration.</li>
						</ol>
					</section>
					<section>
						<span class="icon solid major fa-lock"></span>
						<h3>Why SkillShare Connect?</h3>
						<ol>
							<li>For Volunteers: Share your skills, gain experience, and contribute to causes that align with your values.</li>
							<li>For Organizations: Find the right volunteers for your needs, streamline the recruitment process, and make a lasting impact.</li>
							<li>Seamless Experience: Our platform is easy to use, and our matching system ensures the perfect fit for every opportunity.</li>
						</ol>
					</section>
					<section>
						<span class="icon solid major fa-cog"></span>
						<h3>Our Features</h3>
						<ol>
							<li>Location-Based Matching: Leverage Google Maps to find local opportunities or remote work that fits your schedule.</li>
							<li>Skill-Based Search: Volunteers are matched based on their unique skill sets, ensuring the right person for the right job.</li>
							<li>Manage Your Contributions: Easily track your volunteer hours, see feedback from organizations, and showcase your impact.</li>
							<li>For Businesses and Non-Profits: Post opportunities, manage applicants, and see your initiatives thrive.</li>
						</ol>
					</section>
					<section>
						<span class="icon solid major fa-desktop"></span>
						<h3>Get Involved</h3>
						<p>Volunteers: Ready to make a difference? Join Now!.  Organizations: Need help? Post an Opportunity!</p>

					</section>
					<section>
						<span class="icon solid major fa-link"></span>
